latestPosts.caption:
Dream of 21 years ! 
Presenting your Femina Miss India 2nd RU ! 

Yet I wait for you all to watch my full performance and know that I gave my best, gave my heart and soul 🥹❤️

To my fans and supporters,
Just one thing, I LOVE YOU ALL FOR PRAYING FOR ME AND FOR BEING THERE ! 

I don’t have words to explain how I feel, there is gratitude and I am filled with even more power and 
 BIGGER THINGS WAIT.

More than anything, I wanted to EARN LOVE AND RESPECT and that is what I wanted to be proud of and carry. You all have showered immense of it

 Will live this journey and make most out of it and create a legacy. Stay with me. 
I hope I inspired you all to NEVER GIVE UP.  #UnStoppable 

———
@naughtynatty_g I love you, adore you and is hugely inspired by you. Your words since 2019 have stayed with me and I gave my best to implement everything. I hope to make you even more proud of me … But huge respect for you. Thank you so much 🙏❤️ #bosslady 

@vineetjain12 most approachable for wise words and a leader, don’t know how you do it sir 
Utmost THANK YOU for giving me the START
Your Miss India will make it BIGGER and You’ll be proud. TIMES will be proud #ForeverGratitude 

@varshagupta059 you’re such a leader, your authority and yet caring for nature for us… missing you already and your feedbacks . Thank you ❤️

@bharatg18 you don’t know how much I like you personally and how you are thank you Bharat for always being there …. So much love 🤗 

@hanasayyyed your intelligence beyond age @chandrakant.donde our smart guy there @doshi_yashvi you most caring .. @chetnachodankar your OH my god, 
The best of memories from your guys ❤️

@anuahuja1 your UTTAR PRADESH in 2019 to now, I hope I evolved. Loved your stage guidance to every bit.

@biancalouzado sitting on your chair is the most calming experience 

EVERYONE IN ORG , I AM GRATEFUL. Thank you for shaping me @missindiaorg 
I’ll make you even more proud.

Winning gown  @rohitgandhirahulkhanna 

#MissIndia #UNSTOPPABLE #WayToGo #Gratitude
